{
  "texts": [
    "This study aims to review of ChatGPT for writing scientific manuscripts.",
    "It is weighs ability benefits and issues combined with the integration of the AI model for writing processes and shows valued perceptions of qualifications and limitations to researchers.",
    "The main advantage of using ChatGPT for scientific manuscript writing is the ability to generate manuscript parts.",
    "Researchers can input research results and methods into the model and generate clear and structured manuscripts.",
    "This function significantly reduces the time and work required to create an initial manuscript, allowing researchers to focus on analyzing and reading results [4].ChatGPT is a tool used to produce draft manuscripts to improve language and organize ideas in scientific writing [5]."
  ]
}